{"tid":1385910,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"簡易低成本普及擊退三毛深藍方法","createTime":"2019-07-30T07:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T08:11:02.000Z","uid":141469,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"df95a23b9a41e5d1dbeef8dbecb641131405195c","tid":1385910,"uid":141469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:56:40.000Z","msg":"每次搞親不合作運動，連儂牆 even 機場和平集會都總會有啲三毛深藍廢老廢中出黎指指點點又嘈住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但係面對佢地又唔可以郁手郁腳又唔夠佢地大聲，咁可以點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只需要一個極低成本又易買到嘅道具即可 <br />\n<br />\n登登登～<br />\n就係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">哨子</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/buJD9g4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbuJD9g4.jpg&h=8e701d2f&s={SIZE}\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n只要每次佢地搞搞震同嘈嘅時候吹，加上人數關係，哨子聲一定冚過佢地仲可以做聲音反擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且哨子極多用途：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">和理非遊行可以用黎打拍子、叫口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打機個陣又可以用黎召喚隊友、作行軍拍子同放信號、多人夠大聲又可以當心理技黎震懾敵人<br />\n</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實仲有一個升級嘅道具<br />\n就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">喇叭</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9zFSukb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9zFSukb.jpg&h=b20f4ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">但我就唔係好建議喇</span></strong></span>，因為啲深藍好多時都係上咗年紀，等陣太大聲嚇親佢地又震到佢地耳仔就唔好啦。\b<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4145a47104aaf8b80275b0ccf000b5010b214e2d","tid":1385910,"uid":141469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:58:03.000Z","msg":"一人要一個哨子"},{"pid":"3bc7b0e11e46ea7ac37be86db1fdcf82ccd29697","tid":1385910,"uid":141469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:58:13.000Z","msg":"一人要一個哨子"},{"pid":"d51804e577aff45f55821336acb96f1d1c99ff32","tid":1385910,"uid":141469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:58:23.000Z","msg":"一人要一個哨子"},{"pid":"a75d8bf8dc667b021a9793fe3c9e966a3ee273f7","tid":1385910,"uid":141469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:58:33.000Z","msg":"一人要一個哨子"},{"pid":"014523601eec544dc58f0329ae8a43e840516248","tid":1385910,"uid":141469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:58:43.000Z","msg":"一人要一個哨子"},{"pid":"aff64df45ca909cebc293bf97989231effc9ea1e","tid":1385910,"uid":141469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:58:53.000Z","msg":"一人要一個哨子"},{"pid":"d54af96a44a6669b985a843a4f9eefebf64dd6a4","tid":1385910,"uid":141469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:59:03.000Z","msg":"一人要一個哨子"},{"pid":"bb5ac12fc85cbc5c771e1fbdc0784bfe1c25a953","tid":1385910,"uid":141469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:59:13.000Z","msg":"一人要一個哨子"},{"pid":"e06f40f70f9215b936607d0c898681426629540a","tid":1385910,"uid":141469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:59:23.000Z","msg":"一人要一個哨子"},{"pid":"a41b43d92a8784268b79c348ccaebbbe1ffaed5e","tid":1385910,"uid":141469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:59:33.000Z","msg":"一人要一個哨子"},{"pid":"d4010db43d37c2cce9ef0e1db73ac8121dea5133","tid":1385910,"uid":141469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:59:43.000Z","msg":"一人要一個哨子"},{"pid":"d9e44c927784a93a973add5b71c4fe8a9207adf6","tid":1385910,"uid":141469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited